{
  "stem": "24130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because if they would know, they would take him back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And every time there was, at night, I was so scared to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was afraid they're going to take us away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was in 1941, they took away these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my father came home with the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says that the war-- that they occupied-- they went in-- this, somehow, I remembered, that Germany went to Poland, is occupying Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there are a lot of dead people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was, like, so far away from us, that it didn't affect me so-- so bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when the Hungarians came in, before the Hungarians, the Czechs left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And before the Hungarians came, there were a different government took over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was-- they were called, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- they really said they're going to kill all the Jews-- openly, they said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're going to take over the Jewish property, and they're going to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And who were the [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were boys from the town that we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They grew up, they went-- were older, like, they went with my sisters to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Young boys, they joined this government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they divided-- they already said who's going to take our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I knew this guy that said, I'm going to have your house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father says, he's not going to live to see the-- he's not going to live that long, to have our house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he used to come on Saturday and watch this girl couldn't come in to make fire for us on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
